values:
It's 3/14 1:59, my homage to one of the greatest numbers of all time, PI!
3.14159....... it does so much for us!


Everyone enjoy this most magical of days! :D

Tomorrow the packers (people who pack things, not the football team) are coming to pack up our entire lives into boxes. Including my computer. Which I won't have access to until August 1st when I return from choir trip to Ireland. *sobs, hugs computer to chest* During this period, I will have occasional access to my email, either via brother's laptop or internet cafe's across the country. SO. If you want to keep in touch with me (! which you should) email me at one of two places: 1. [myFirstName].[myLastName]@gmail.com - this is the one I check more often, and it's only for "real life" interactions, not forums and stuff. So this is the best way to reach me (don't forget the dot . in between the names!). 2. If you don't know my last name (for some reason?) email me at [myLiveJournalName]@gmail.com So adieu until August!

Okay, so I know I said I would never ever post in my Livejournal, and I intend on keeping that promise, but oh wow this meme was too good to pass up. Friends Question Quiz (don't take it too seriously) 1.~How did you meet rentheadnlewy? I sat in front of him in Freshman Biology (wow almost FOUR YEARS AGO) and made fun of him for allegedly grinding with some girl at winter formal dance. Heehee. 2.~What would you do if you had never met contrivereality? Ummmm not have ever rocked out to Eminem on the way to Into the Woods rehersal? Actually no, I might've done that, it just would've been a lot sadder. 3.~What do you honestly think of midgetcatcher? Dan is the coolest guy ever. He is so talented and professional and straightforward and NICE. Wait, midgetcatcher is Dan right? *checks* Oh phew. It is. 4.~Would or did morrigan1212 and warholswhore go out? Haaaa!!!! No, but that'd be funny if they did. Luke! Amy! Awwww... 5.~Have you ever liked demon_dunce? Not... like THAT! =\ 6.~If halyiaganitefiz died tomorrow, what is one thing that you would need him/her to know? OMG ALY I LOVE YOU! I have the biggest non-crush crush on you! <3<3 You rock and are hilarious and fantastic! WIZARD AND I! *air pianos* 7.~Would radstude and brendantheking make a good couple? *strokes chin* ... possibly... possibly. 8.~Describe zozerzs in 3 words: Younger than me? 9.~Do you think rainb0w_carnage is hot? Hmmmm I suppose. :P 10.~Would halyiaganitefiz and phaedra_amunet make a lovely couple? Probably not. They're both pretty funny, but (1) they've never met, (2) the age difference, and (3) Aly already has a boy/man/thing! 11.~What do you think of when you see warholswhore? HAPPY LUKE! And stop smoking! *cough* =P 12.~Tell me something humiliating about brendantheking: Ummmmm... he's on the ski team? That's embarrassing, right? 13.~Do you know any of thomas_wynd's family members? Wow, like, all of them. Except for... no wait, I did meet Margaret (the SECRET step-sister). Dang. Now it's on to extended family, eh? 14.~What's rainb0w_carnage's favorite color? UM... rainbow? *lame* 15.~On a scale of 1-10 how cute is schmackyferrit? Eight. 16.~What would you do if sparkly_dark just professed their undying love for you? Look inquisitively at Mug-z and then back away slowly. 17.~What language does morrigan1212 speak? English and KNITTER! :D 18.~Who is rainb0w_carnage going out with? Um.... a boy? Oh I dunno. 19.~Is clarkiebabe03 a boy or a girl? A girl! Duh. 20.~Would aspiring_loser and sparkly_dark make a good couple? ... dun think so. 21.~Who do you think rodstewartishot would be great with from this list? Me! No, I don't really know. 22.~When was the last time you talked to rainb0w_carnage? Oh wow..... hmmm.... months ago. Geez... 23.~What is demon_dunce's favorite band? That one with the rockability! 24.~Does radstude have any siblings? No... ? Wait! Yes! Little Shutters! I saw him at Ryan's party! 25.~Would you ever date thomas_wynd? Nope. 26.~Would you ever date zozerzs? Nope. 27.~Is rodstewartishot single? Yep? 28.~What is rainb0w_carnage's last name? Lehrmen. (Atrocious spelling, I know) 29.~What is aspiring_loser's middle name? Jesus? 30~What is midgetcatcher's fantasy? Taking Steph in the back of DS theatre. Totally. 31.~Where does clarkiebabe03 live? Way the heck out! In Arrowhead-land! 32.~Would you make out with rentheadnlewy? *shifty eyes* =P 33.~Are contrivereality and thomas_wynd best friends? Not that I know of. 34.~Does zozerzs like rainb0w_carnage? Have they ever met?? 35.~How did you meet aspiring_loser? Friend of a friend, no? 36.~Is rainb0w_carnage older than you? Probably. 37.~Is phaedra_amunet the sexiest person alive? Well duh. All ARGers rock the sexiness. That's why we play games where we can meet OTHER sexy people. Okay.... so how often have I been posting? Every eight months or so? Don't expect me to keep THAT up. *snorts*

Alright. This is my LiveJournal. It is not for posting. Do not expect me to post here. Do not visit here and wonder why I have not posted. Do not contact me and ask me why I do not post. I am telling you right here. I did not sign up for this to post. The only exception I will make to this rule is the LJ community ~knitting, as a demonstration of my old woman-ism. This is also for my friends list, because they have livejournals and like to post. And I'm darn sick of typing in all of their usernames! =D Karl
